<paragraph blockId="25.[264,1323,1311,1897]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,583,1751,1777]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">General distribution:</emphasis>
Another wide ranging species from Newfoundland west to 
<collectingRegion box="[264,340,1791,1817]" country="Canada" name="Yukon" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Yukon</collectingRegion>
and south to GSMNP and west to 
<collectingRegion box="[755,859,1791,1817]" country="United States of America" name="Missouri" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Missouri</collectingRegion>
in the East and southern 
<collectingRegion isEnumeration="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">New Mexico, Arizona</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion box="[422,541,1831,1857]" country="United States of America" name="California" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">California</collectingRegion>
in the West.
</paragraph>
